Fingerprint Unlock
Fingerprint Unlock creates a unique model of your fingerprint to verify it’s you. To create this fingerprint model during setup, you will take images of your fingerprint from different positions.

When you use Fingerprint Unlock, images are used to update your fingerprint model. Images used to create your fingerprint model are never stored, but the fingerprint model is stored securely on your tablet and never leaves the tablet. All processing occurs securely on your tablet.
You can delete your fingerprint model, or turn off Fingerprint Unlock at any time in Settings. Fingerprint models are stored on the tablet until you delete them.

Fingerprint Unlock creates a unique model of your child’s fingerprint to verify it’s them. To create this fingerprint model during setup, they will take images of their fingerprint from different positions.

When they use Fingerprint Unlock, images are used to update their fingerprint model. Images used to create your child’s fingerprint model are never stored, but the fingerprint model is stored securely on the tablet and never leaves the tablet. All processing occurs securely on the tablet.
You and your child can delete their fingerprint model, or turn off Fingerprint Unlock at any time in Settings. Fingerprint models are stored on the tablet until they’re deleted.
